                    "Thermal Image Processing",
                    color = Color(0xFF7D8590),
                    fontSize = 18.sp,
                    fontWeight = FontWeight.Medium
                )
                Text(
                    "Algorithm: $selectedAlgorithm",
                    color = Color(0xFFFF6B35),
                    fontSize = 14.sp
                )
            }
        }
    }
}

@Composable
private fun ProcessingOverlay(
